2 desperate to escape. But with a tremendous roar,\u8232 Scamander\'92s flood rushed on in pursuit behind him.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0310\u8232 Just as a man laying out a ditch from a dark spring\u8232 to his plants and gardens digs a water channel,\u8232 mattock in hand, removing what obstructs the flow,\u8232 and the water, as it starts to run, pushes aside\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[260]\u8232 the pebbles, and then, gaining momentum, flows down\u8232 and overtakes the man who\'92s guiding it\'97\u8232 that\'92s how the flooding wave kept clutching at Achilles\u8232 for all his speed, since gods have much more strength than men.\u8232 Every time swift-footed, godlike Achilles\u8232 tried stopping to fight back, to see if all the gods\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0320\u8232 who live in spacious heaven were forcing him to flee,\u8232 a tremendous wave from that heaven-fed river\u8232 would crash down around his shoulders. He\'92d jump clear,\u8232 heart panicking, but the river kept tugging at his legs\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[270]\u8232 with a strong undertow, washing out the ground\u8232 beneath his feet. Then gazing up into the wide sky\u8232 the son of Peleus cried out:\
