e, so he\'92d think\u8232 he could catch up. Meanwhile, the other Trojans\u8232 fleeing in confusion, came crowding in the city,\u8232 throngs of them, cramming the gates, happy to be there.\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0730\u8232 They didn\'92t dare to wait outside the wall, to check\u8232 who made it back and who had perished in the fight.\u8232 They streamed into the city in an eager rush,\u8232 all whose legs and knees had brought them safely in.\
